                    <td colspan="3" align="left"> <h3 class="h3">Welcome</h3></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr> 
                    <td colspan="2" align="left" valign="top"><div align="center"> 
                        <div align="justify"> <font size="3" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">First 
                          Church of Christ, Scientist, Edmonton is a welcoming 
                          place of worship in downtown Edmonton. Its services 
                          and Reading Room are open to anyone who is seeking healing, 
                          searching for direction and answers to spiritual questions, 
                          or simply wishing to join with others in acknowledging 
                          God's loving care.</font> <font size="3"></h3> </font></h3> 
                        </div>
                        <p align="justify"><font size="3" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The 
                          Edmonton church is one of many Christian Science churches 
                          throughout the world. It is a branch of The First Church 
                          of Christ, Scientist in Boston, Massachusetts. The Church 
                          of Christ, Scientist was founded by Mary Baker Eddy 
                          to &quot;commemorate the word and works of our Master&quot;&#8212;Christ 
                          Jesus&#8212;and to &quot;reinstate primitive Christianity 
                          and its lost element of healing.&quot;</font></p>
                        <p><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><a href="sunday.htm#lesson" target="_parent"><img src="images/This-Sunday-Banner.jpg" width="328" height="77" border="0"></a></strong></font></p>
                        <p><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><a href="events.htm" target="_parent"><img src="images/Events-News-Button.gif" width="329" height="77" border="0"></a></strong></font></p>
                        <p><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><a href="wednesday.htm#WedRead" target="_self"><img src="images/Wed-Readings-Button.gif" width="328" height="78" border="0"></a></strong></font></p>
                      </div></td>
                    <td width="262" height="50" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><img src="images/indexANIM-7-11.gif" width="262" height="382" vspace="8"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/csedmonton" target="_blank"><img src="images/Facebook%20Like.jpg" width="262" height="92" vspace="6" border="0"></a></p></td>
