                    <td width="314" height="54" align="left" valign="middle"> 
                      <h2 class="h2">Reading Room</h2>
                      <font size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Our 
                      Reading Room is located in the same building as the church. 
                      It is a place to study and learn more about Christian Science. 
                      <br>
                      <br>
                      The Reading Room is open on <strong>Wednesday</strong> from 
                      <strong>1:00 to 4:30 PM</strong>, <strong>Friday</strong> 
                      from <strong>11:00 AM to 3:00 PM</strong> and also <strong>after 
                      the Sunday service</strong>.</font> <font color="#666666" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The 
                      entrance is on 100 Avenue.</font> <p></p>
                      <p align="center"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a style="text-decoration:none;color:#666666" href="readingroom.htm" target="_parent"><strong><em>Click 
                        here for more information</em></strong></a></font></p></td>
