                  <tr> 
                    <td height="54" colspan="3" align="left" valign="top"><h2 class="h2">Location</h2>
                      <p align="justify"><font size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">The 
                        church and Reading Room are located at the corner of 100 
                        Avenue and 108 Street (10810 100 Avenue). It is one block 
                        south of Jasper Avenue and the Corona LRT Station (108 
                        Street exit). </font></p>
                      <p align="justify"><font size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">There 
                        is free parking available for the Sunday service and Wednesday 
                        meeting in the church lot on the north side of the building. 
                        During the day there is limited parking available for 
                        Reading Room patrons and visitors on church business. 
                        Please ask the Reading room attendant about where to park.</font></p>
                      <p align="center"><font color="#666666" size="2" face="Geneva, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><a style="text-decoration:none;color:#666666" href="location.htm" target="_parent"><strong><em>Click 
